{"title":" 二次请求的错误","date":"2018-06-11T03:05:00.000Z","link":"post/121","categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:25:10.132Z","content":"<p>  第一次html请求是get请求 所以会直接执行 include $this-&gt;template()。这样就会直接执行 <strong>2html </strong>页面。但是 <strong>2html</strong> 的<code>&lt;input type=&#39;hidden&#39; name=&#39;id&#39; value=&#39;{$id}&#39; /&gt;</code>并没有获得id值。<strong>因为第一次html请求的值并没有包含进去</strong>，需要定义一个<code>$id = $_GPC[&#39;id&#39;];</code>。这样就和 <strong>2html</strong>的<code>value=&#39;{$id}&#39;</code>就会获得值。当 <strong>2html</strong> 进行<strong> post请求</strong>时，后台php就会更新。从而更新数据库。</p>\n<p>而我第一次写的时候，并没有定义<code>$id = $_GPC[&#39;id&#39;];</code> 。这样就导致了 2html 中的<code>value=&#39;{$id}&#39;</code>，取不到值，当 <strong>2html</strong> 进行<strong> post请求</strong>时php后台也去不到<strong>id</strong>的值，这样虽然页面刷新，但数据没有更新。</p>\n<h3 id=\"1html\">1html<a href=\"post/121#1html\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a  class=&apos;btn btn-default btn-sm&apos;  data-toggle=&quot;ajaxModal&quot;  href=&quot;&#123;php echo webUrl(&apos;share/exchangelist/remarksaler&apos;, array(&apos;id&apos; =&gt; $item[&apos;id&apos;]))&#125;&quot; title=&quot;不通过申请&quot;&gt;&lt;i class=&apos;fa fa-remove&apos;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">请求url 把id传到后台php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"后台php\">后台php<a href=\"post/121#后台php\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">public function remarksaler() </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tglobal $_W;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tglobal $_GPC;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                $id = $_GPC[&apos;id&apos;];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                $item = pdo_fetch(&apos;select * from &apos;.tablename(&apos;weikang_deposit_refund&apos;).&apos; where uniacid =:uniacid and id =:id &apos;,array(&apos;id&apos; =&gt; $_GPC[&apos;id&apos;], &apos;uniacid&apos; =&gt; $_W[&apos;uniacid&apos;]));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tif ($_W[&apos;ispost&apos;]) </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#123;       </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tpdo_update(&apos;weikang_deposit_refund&apos;, array(&apos;fail_message&apos; =&gt; $_GPC[&apos;remark&apos;],&apos;draw_status&apos; =&gt; 2), array(&apos;id&apos; =&gt; $_GPC[&apos;id&apos;], &apos;uniacid&apos; =&gt; $_W[&apos;uniacid&apos;]));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tshow_json(1,array(&quot;url&quot;=&gt;webUrl(&apos;share/exchangelist&apos;)));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tinclude $this-&gt;template();</span><br><span class=\"line\">               </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2html\">2html<a href=\"post/121#2html\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;form class=&quot;form-horizontal form-validate&quot; action=&quot;&#123;php echo webUrl(&apos;share/exchangelist/remarksaler&apos;)&#125;&quot; method=&quot;post&quot; enctype=&quot;multipart/form-data&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;input type=&apos;hidden&apos; name=&apos;id&apos; value=&apos;&#123;$id&#125;&apos; /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;div class=&quot;modal-dialog&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           &lt;div class=&quot;modal-content&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div class=&quot;modal-header&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;button data-dismiss=&quot;modal&quot; class=&quot;close&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;×&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;h4 class=&quot;modal-title&quot;&gt;失败原因&lt;/h4&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div class=&quot;modal-body&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &lt;textarea style=&quot;height:150px;&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; name=&quot;remark&quot;  placeholder=&quot;失败原因&quot; &gt;&#123;$item[&apos;fail_message&apos;]&#125;&lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div class=&quot;modal-footer&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-primary&quot; type=&quot;submit&quot;&gt;提交&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;button data-dismiss=&quot;modal&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;取消&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/form&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"log4j基础知识","link":"post/123"},"next":{"title":"php 中empty和isset的区别","link":"post/119"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/121/"}